# EAS Build archive ignore — this monorepo holds many unrelated subprojects, but
# the ONLY EAS project is ifinance-mobile/. EAS roots the upload archive at this
# folder (the git root), so without this file it copies the whole tree — which
# fails on otbi-atd/.otbi_runner.lock (EBUSY, held by the running OTBI runner) and
# needlessly uploads other apps' source. Exclude every sibling; keep ifinance-mobile.
#
# NOTE: when EAS finds a .easignore it uses THIS file instead of .gitignore, so we
# must also re-exclude the mobile app's node_modules/build dirs here.

# ── Monorepo siblings (not part of the mobile app) ──────────────────────────
/apps/
/assessment-3/
/db/
/docs/
/final apps/
/myDoc/
/otbi-atd/

# ── Root-level files we don't need in the build ─────────────────────────────
*.log
*.lock
.otbi_runner.lock

# ── Inside ifinance-mobile: deps + generated/native dirs (mirror its .gitignore)
ifinance-mobile/node_modules/
ifinance-mobile/.expo/
ifinance-mobile/dist/
ifinance-mobile/dist-check/
ifinance-mobile/ios/
ifinance-mobile/android/
ifinance-mobile/web-build/
